/*!
 * @page top_readme Project README
 *
 * The repo-root @c README.md is reproduced below as a regular Doxygen
 * page.  Doxygen's `IMPLICIT_DIR_DOCS = YES` (kept on so that
 * `include/triggers/README.md` and friends still serve as directory
 * docs) would otherwise treat the top-level README as the description
 * of the repo-root dir — which Doxygen doesn't scan — and the content
 * would land nowhere.  This wrapper sidesteps that by giving the
 * README an explicit page id so it gets a real HTML page.
 *
 * `EXAMPLE_PATH` is set to `..` in Doxyfile so the relative path below
 * resolves from the project root.
 *
 * @include README.md
 */
